---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Au Pair Research">

<!-- Header -->
<section style="padding-top:3rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
    <span style="font-size:1.5rem;">🏡</span>
    <h1 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,6vw,2.5rem);line-height:1.1;color:var(--gold);margin:0;">
      Au Pair Research
    </h1>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin:0;">
    Dima + Jeannie Perkis · Dean ~3.5yo, Ruby ~15mo · Atlanta VA-Highland
  </p>
</section>

<!-- The Problem -->
<section style="margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:2rem;padding:1.5rem;background:var(--surface);border-left:3px solid var(--gold);border:1px solid var(--border);">
  <h2 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);margin:0 0 .75rem;">
    The Problem
  </h2>
  <p style="font-size:.875rem;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">
    Evenings are depleted. After daycare pickup through bedtime, there's no bandwidth left for Jeannie + Dima connection, Dean's attention, or personal reset.
  </p>
  <p style="font-size:.875rem;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.65;margin:.75rem 0 0;">
    This is a <strong style="color:var(--gold);">capacity problem, not a relationship problem</strong> — confirmed through coaching sessions with Eric.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Cost Scenarios -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Cost Scenarios</h2>
  <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 1rem;">
    Current baseline: Daycare + babysitter + cleaning = <strong style="color:var(--ink);">$4,004/mo ($48,048/yr)</strong>
  </p>

  <!-- Scenario A -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <span style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--ink);">A: Layer On Top</span>
      <span style="font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.15em .5em;background:#8b0000;color:#fff;border-radius:2px;">NOT VIABLE</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">
      <div><span style="color:var(--muted);">$74,587–77,887/yr</span> · <span style="color:var(--muted);">+$2,211–2,486/mo delta</span></div>
      <div>Surplus: <span style="color:var(--muted);">$635–910/mo</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scenario B -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <span style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--ink);">B: Replace Sitter Only</span>
      <span style="font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.15em .5em;border:1px solid #8a6012;color:#8a6012;border-radius:2px;">TIGHT</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">
      <div><span style="color:var(--muted);">$68,971–72,271/yr</span> · <span style="color:var(--muted);">+$1,743–2,018/mo delta</span></div>
      <div>Surplus: <span style="color:var(--muted);">$1,103–1,378/mo</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scenario C (Recommended) -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid var(--gold);margin-bottom:.75rem;position:relative;">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:0;right:0;background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.2em .6em;font-weight:bold;">RECOMMENDED</div>
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <span style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--gold);">C: Replace Sitter + Date Nights ✓</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">
      <div><span style="color:var(--ink);font-weight:bold;">$65,971–69,271/yr</span> · <span style="color:var(--ink);font-weight:bold;">+$1,493–1,768/mo delta</span></div>
      <div>Surplus: <span style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:bold;">$1,353–1,628/mo</span> · <strong style="color:var(--ink);">BALANCED</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scenario D -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem;margin-bottom:.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <span style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--ink);">D: Replace Dean Daycare</span>
      <span style="font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.15em .5em;border:1px solid #c44;color:#c44;border-radius:2px;">MAX HOURS RISK</span>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">
      <div><span style="color:var(--muted);">$55,711–59,011/yr</span> · <span style="color:var(--muted);">+$640–915/mo delta</span></div>
      <div>Surplus: <span style="color:var(--muted);">$2,206–2,481/mo</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--gold);margin:1rem 0 0;padding:.75rem;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:2px;">
    Year 2 surplus under Scenario C jumps to ~$2,300–2,600/mo.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Agency Comparison -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Agency Comparison</h2>

  <!-- Go Au Pair -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1.5px solid var(--gold);margin-bottom:.75rem;position:relative;">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:0;right:0;background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);font-size:.6rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:.2em .6em;font-weight:bold;">★ RECOMMENDED</div>
    <h3 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);margin:0 0 .25rem;">
      Go Au Pair
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 .5rem;">
      ~$21,574/yr · <a href="https://community.goaupair.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--violet);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">community.goaupair.com/register</a> · (888) 287-2471
    </p>
    <ul style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;padding-left:1.25rem;line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Accenture $100 discount</li>
      <li>Profile in 7 days $150 off</li>
      <li>Price match guarantee</li>
      <li>Pro-rated refund</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Au Pair in America -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <h3 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 .25rem;">
      Au Pair in America (AIFS)
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 .5rem;">
      ~$21,839/yr · <a href="https://aupairinamerica.com/forms/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--violet);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">aupairinamerica.com/forms/register</a> · (800) 928-7247
    </p>
    <ul style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;padding-left:1.25rem;line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Largest agency (40 yrs)</li>
      <li>Most established</li>
      <li>Self-service portal</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Cultural Care -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <h3 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 .25rem;">
      Cultural Care
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 .5rem;">
      ~$21,500–22,000/yr · <a href="https://culturalcare.com/becoming-a-host-family/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--violet);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">culturalcare.com/becoming-a-host-family/</a> · (800) 333-6056
    </p>
    <ul style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;padding-left:1.25rem;line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Dedicated Matching Specialist</li>
      <li>Mobile app</li>
      <li>Promo: <code style="background:var(--bg);padding:.1em .4em;border-radius:2px;font-size:.75rem;color:var(--gold);">PCREGWA</code></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- InterExchange -->
  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
    <h3 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--ink);margin:0 0 .25rem;">
      InterExchange
    </h3>
    <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 .5rem;">
      ~$21,500–22,000/yr · <a href="https://app.aupairusa.org/host-family-apply" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--violet);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">app.aupairusa.org/host-family-apply</a> · (800) 287-2477
    </p>
    <ul style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;padding-left:1.25rem;line-height:1.7;">
      <li>Nonprofit</li>
      <li>Fast: 5 weeks match-to-arrival</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Process Timeline -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Process Timeline</h2>

  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--border);">
    {[
      { step: '1', title: 'Register (FREE)', desc: '10 min, browse profiles immediately', duration: '' },
      { step: '2', title: 'Build Profile', desc: '"Dear Au Pair" letter + photos', duration: '1–2 hours' },
      { step: '3', title: 'Screening', desc: 'In-home interview, background checks', duration: '1–2 weeks' },
      { step: '4', title: 'Search & Match', desc: 'Browse, interview, extend offer', duration: '1–4 weeks' },
      { step: '5', title: 'Visa & Arrival', desc: 'Agency handles paperwork', duration: '5–12 weeks' },
    ].map((item, i) => (
      <div style={`display:flex;gap:1rem;${i < 4 ? 'padding-bottom:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);' : ''}`}>
        <div style="flex-shrink:0;width:2rem;height:2rem;background:var(--gold);color:var(--bg);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:.9rem;font-weight:bold;">
          {item.step}
        </div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:.15rem;">{item.title}</div>
          <div style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin:0;">{item.desc}{item.duration ? ` · ${item.duration}` : ''}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
  <p style="font-size:.825rem;color:var(--gold);margin:1rem 0 0;padding:.75rem;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:2px;">
    Total: ~8–12 weeks from today to arrival (July–August 2026)
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Action Checklist -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Action Checklist</h2>

  <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.5rem;border:1px solid var(--border);">
    {[
      { done: false, text: 'Register with Go Au Pair (FREE)', link: 'https://community.goaupair.com/register' },
      { done: false, text: 'Register with Au Pair in America (FREE)', link: 'https://aupairinamerica.com/forms/register' },
      { done: false, text: 'Browse profiles (infant experience)' },
      { done: false, text: 'Call both agencies for info' },
      { done: false, text: 'Write "Dear Au Pair" letter together' },
      { done: false, text: 'Take photos: kids, home, au pair room, bathroom' },
      { done: false, text: 'Complete full profiles on both platforms' },
      { done: false, text: 'Identify 2 references (David? Ben? coworker?)' },
      { done: false, text: 'Get employment verification (Lahzo, CHOA)' },
      { done: false, text: 'Decide which agency to commit to' },
    ].map(item => (
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:.75rem;padding:.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
        <span style="flex-shrink:0;width:1.25rem;height:1.25rem;border:2px solid var(--border-hi);border-radius:2px;margin-top:.15rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
        </span>
        <div>
          {item.link ? (
            <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--violet);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">
              {item.text} ↗
            </a>
          ) : (
            <span style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--ink);">{item.text}</span>
          )}
        </div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Key Q&As -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
  <h2 style="font-size:.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.15em;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem;">Key Q&As</h2>

  {[
    {
      q: 'Can we afford it?',
      a: 'Scenario C adds $1,493–1,768/mo but replaces fragmented sitter coordination with consistent coverage. Year 2 surplus jumps to ~$2,300–2,600/mo.'
    },
    {
      q: 'Where would they live?',
      a: 'Basement room at Morningside — private bedroom with door. Bathroom: can share with kids but NOT parents. Need to confirm egress window (State Dept requirement).'
    },
    {
      q: 'Is it safe?',
      a: 'Background checks, 3+ references, in-home interviews, psychological evaluation, English test. State Dept regulated (BridgeUSA J-1 visa). Local rep checks in monthly.'
    },
    {
      q: 'What if it doesn\'t work out?',
      a: 'Rematch process (~2 weeks). Pro-rated refund. Industry rematch rate: ~20–30%.'
    },
    {
      q: 'What would they actually do?',
      a: 'Mornings: help get kids ready, breakfast, daycare drop-off. Evenings: pickup, dinner, bath, bedtime. Weekends: one 6–8 hr block. Cannot do: general housework, cooking for adults, pet care.'
    },
    {
      q: 'How many hours?',
      a: 'Max 45 hrs/week, max 10 hrs/day. 1.5 consecutive days off per week. One full weekend off per month.'
    },
  ].map(qa => (
    <div style="background:var(--surface);padding:1.25rem;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:.75rem;">
      <h3 style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--gold);margin:0 0 .5rem;">{qa.q}</h3>
      <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;margin:0;">{qa.a}</p>
    </div>
  ))}
</section>

<!-- Bottom Line -->
<section style="margin-bottom:2rem;padding:1.5rem;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--gold);">
  <p style="font-family:'DM Serif Display',serif;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--ink);margin:0;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;">
    <a href="https://community.goaupair.com/register" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-style:dotted;text-underline-offset:2px;">Register now</a> (free, 10 min) → browse profiles → match in 1–3 weeks → au pair arrives <strong style="color:var(--gold);">July–August 2026</strong>.
  </p>
</section>

</Layout>
